{"tid":1620120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我地接受左蒙面法，其他惡法會陸續有黎","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T09:35:34.000Z","uid":184597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b48a87e437b2ece69a18c40c9d09766e8fca612c","tid":1620120,"uid":184597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"純討論<br />\n<br />\n政府試水溫，初次引用緊急法，推出既，係好似好合理、多個國家都有實施既蒙面法。蒙面法對和理非既影響當然相當之大，但成件事既重點，其實係引用緊急法。<br />\n<br />\n一不離二，二變三，三變無窮。若果和理非正中下懷，因蒙面法而卻步，拒絕帶口罩，拒絕上街，咁就完美配合左政府既劇本。而政府亦會因此信心大增，一連串打擊抗爭既舉操必定陸續有黎：凍結抗爭基金，鎖區，封internet，擴大警權，上門搜查⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我想問問各位和理非，您地諗清楚要點面對未？"},{"pid":"4106071d28acb2c9941150a54717a9fd5874dc76","tid":1620120,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"帶口罩呀，全部放工放學帶翻上個口度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日怕尷尬唔帶，聽日比人拉冇得帶呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1620074/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1620074/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aOXOHjJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaOXOHjJ.jpg&h=5d2bcd89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b707ecd4e7453e3b57e2275649b2ec54c7bcc7ef","tid":1620120,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"大家好似對緊急法無乜感覺<br />\n俾政府spin左落去一條無撚用既蒙面法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910d6923d00cc4dccb300768e9e89f5b15e8d23d","tid":1620120,"uid":241363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:35:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n驅逐共匪 香港獨立</span></span>"}]}